title: blog: gofix examples are 404ing
body:
What happened?
Visited
https://code.google.com/p/go/source/browse/src/cmd/gofix/netdial.go
which is linked to from
http://blog.golang.org/introducing-gofix
and it returns error 404 not found.


What should have happened instead?
Wanted to see the example netdial.go gofix page


Please provide any additional information below.
All of the linked examples are 404ing.
